And don't fucking look at me like that.

237
00:26:26,868 --> 00:26:28,335
I did not do it.

238
00:26:28,503 --> 00:26:31,165
- Who did?
- It's obvious.

239
00:26:32,007 --> 00:26:33,907
Fucking pigs. Ha.

240
00:26:34,075 --> 00:26:37,670
- They must not have liked your demands.
- I didn't make any demands, all right?

241
00:26:37,846 --> 00:26:42,249
Do you think I'm fucking stupid?
The police don't kill hostages, you idiot.

242
00:26:42,550 --> 00:26:46,509
- Why? Why did you do it?
- Have you lost your mind?

243
00:26:46,688 --> 00:26:49,748
