The doors open.

244
00:26:49,924 --> 00:26:53,121
Big scissors. Head comes off. Here it is.

245
00:26:55,263 --> 00:26:56,958
Hey... Hey, hey, hey. That is my gun.

246
00:26:57,132 --> 00:27:00,624
