247
00:27:01,069 --> 00:27:02,627
You tell me the truth now.

248
00:27:03,104 --> 00:27:06,904
Look at me. Eh? Look at my hands.

249
00:27:07,509 --> 00:27:11,206
If I'd have cut his head off,
I would have been covered in blood.

250
