there is a hell of a mess.

251
00:27:15,784 --> 00:27:18,150
Ask them. Ask them!

252
00:27:18,320 --> 00:27:21,585
And then I want an apology
and my gun back.

253
00:27:21,756 --> 00:27:24,384
You'll get your gun
when we make it out of here.

254
00:27:24,559 --> 00:27:26,424
<i>- Can you hear me? Hello.
Yes.</i>

255
00:27:26,594 --> 00:27:29,654
<i>Sorry about what happened
to the man you sent. That was a mistake.</i>

256
00:27:29,831 --> 00:27:31,560
See? Huh. See?

257
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:34,463
