You cut his fucking head off.

258
00:27:34,636 --> 00:27:35,796
<i>I know, it was a tragedy.</i>

259
00:27:35,970 --> 00:27:39,667
<i>Still, you do have other hostages,
don't you?</i>

260
00:27:40,008 --> 00:27:42,033
<i>- Yeah.
- Send another one along.</i>

261
00:27:42,210 --> 00:27:46,237
<i>This time a woman.
I'll give you 10 minutes.</i>

262
00:27:46,948 --> 00:27:48,347
So, what they say? Eh?

263
00:27:48,516 --> 00:27:50,609
They want another hostage.
They want a woman.

264
00:27:50,985 --> 00:27:54,148
- Well, you take her.
- No.

265
00:27:55,090 --> 00:27:59,390
No. Nobody's taking anyone anywhere.
I wanna check something.

266
00:27:59,561 --> 00:28:01,961
Don't do anything until I come back.

267
00:28:02,697 --> 00:28:04,722
Sit here with my head.

268
00:28:27,489 --> 00:28:28,751
Ah...

269
00:29:54,008 --> 00:29:56,841
Hey. Ha-ha-ha.

270
00:30:15,463 --> 00:30:18,762
- You calmed down?
- As if you care.

271
00:30:26,741 --> 00:30:28,299
Fucking coward.

272
00:30:28,610 --> 00:30:30,635
When are you going to let
the rest of us go?

273
