280
00:30:52,867 --> 00:30:55,267
Just shut up.
Everybody just shut up, okay?

281
00:30:55,436 --> 00:30:58,928
- Hey, Ritchie, get a grip of yourself.
- Is he all right?

282
00:31:02,110 --> 00:31:04,340
Okay, this is my fault.

283
00:31:04,512 --> 00:31:06,844
You want to know what happened
to the young man.

284
00:31:07,382 --> 00:31:08,940
The police, they picked him up.

285
00:31:09,751 --> 00:31:12,948
His last words to me were,
"Tell all of my new friends. "

286
00:31:13,121 --> 00:31:14,315
That's all of you.

287
00:31:14,489 --> 00:31:17,117
"I will meet you in the bar
for a drink later. "

288
00:31:17,292 --> 00:31:19,192
Peter, Peter, outside. Now.

289
00:31:23,031 --> 00:31:27,730
Was it just me or did anyone else
see the head?

290
