I've seen heads.

291
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:41,380
Christ.

292
00:31:43,351 --> 00:31:45,945
I've seen hundreds of them.

293
00:32:00,702 --> 00:32:05,935
Let me introduce myself.
Bogdanovich, Boris.

294
00:32:06,107 --> 00:32:10,168
Serial number 881967.

295
00:32:10,378 --> 00:32:13,108
Ex-Spetsnaz Special Forces.

296
00:32:13,348 --> 00:32:19,617
