472
00:45:25,873 --> 00:45:27,306
Sit.

473
00:45:31,311 --> 00:45:36,715
- Please. You don't have to do this.
- Yuri, tie him up.

474
00:46:12,052 --> 00:46:13,451
Get away from the door.

475
00:46:17,024 --> 00:46:21,290
There's only one of them.
She's scared, just talk to her.

476
00:46:29,736 --> 00:46:34,571
Look, I don't know what's going on
but I just want to go home.

477
00:46:35,576 --> 00:46:38,875
- Why don't you open the door?
- I can't.

